{"tid":1942282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解熱門日都係d抗爭以外post","createTime":"2020-03-25T03:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T08:21:07.000Z","uid":110125,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"04b5f4c274a756a9a4a87f77fca8d4c4959e075d","tid":1942282,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"日日情色Post都上到熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1942241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1942241</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地有冇發現，上熱門嘅post唔一定好多留言，就算你地點樣推推拉拉都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑同click rate有好大關連。熱門好多時都係係標題到清楚易明，例如鹹濕post，標題黨呢啲post都好易上到熱門。 亦都某程度上證明左一班為數唔多嘅單一用戶對個post做嘅action，例如click入去，正皮，留言，對個post上熱門冇乜大幫助。<br />\n<br />\n因為時事總係愈新愈突發愈有吸引力，所以你地停推啲舊post/幾個人推post係冇乜用。加上你地阻止唔到所謂&ldquo;Pr公司開廢post&rdquo;，<span style=\"color: red;\">不如你地放棄個熱門，叫啲人養成入cc台睇post啦</span>。要睇嘅自然會睇，唔睇嘅就算熱門成版都係，佢都會碌番去吹水台。<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係俾啲創意，唔好郁啲就屌哂人地老母，咁樣只會冇人click入你個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d935828a6990f4b3699b053215bb28543c8125","tid":1942282,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"人地個post都上左熱門啦 得30幾個留言"},{"pid":"3feee4b8982065c5aa6bc50736ba18ffb14da9a9","tid":1942282,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人明"},{"pid":"4106b45acdae2a834bc2a923a832d8d650ca2eb1","tid":1942282,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"我個標題開得衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5711bcff5a1bbcf293b77910b2d62ab90a06aa38","tid":1942282,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"平時冇睇熱門, 睇開吹水台"},{"pid":"07fd40523d45c64ca524899d9af3e554f0633cba","tid":1942282,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲入嚟慢慢睇，好少睇熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1f59fe53ea20eb82aeda8c7c71b0b8a938386c","tid":1942282,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"大家態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043ae32022d18eec3b438c627a777144e88b5889","tid":1942282,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地老母"},{"pid":"a63905110e43ffe02d37f2674d470e32c4cacb7f","tid":1942282,"uid":9566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"其實淨係睇熱門好ON9 有時有D話題 手法 資訊等等 都係可以長期討論 / 需要講好耐先有答案<br />\n但係你熱門都係一時三刻 慣左睇熱門可能就只會就咁碌一眼就算吸收唔到 <br />\n但係如果定時定侯入返時事台 就好似波台APPS台咁入返果個TOPIC繼續討論上次未講完既野<br />\n得出黎既結果同埋討論過程一定會更加好"},{"pid":"eff0171047ba066d2d0f60ad9db7823d9e7e37c2","tid":1942282,"uid":12824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"有心睇抗爭post嘅人過咗咁多個月都會入時事台睇點會喺熱門睇<br />\n唔想睇個啲就算上咗熱門都唔會睇<br />\n唔明咁執著個熱門做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c8d384ff5ca27c49e61284fea120aaea45c80a","tid":1942282,"uid":133525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你地老母，我宣布以後熱門只可以有抗爭po，如果發現有其他po，就唔該即刻report ，再用不推文覆話五毛同分化撚"},{"pid":"118918156384b791ee4da4174684bb13b442c2bd","tid":1942282,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔睇熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25985c7f7639c10231e40e1539b44feb1fa10a4b","tid":1942282,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5711bcff5a1bbcf293b77910b2d62ab90a06aa38","tid":1942282,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"平時冇睇熱門, 睇開吹水台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"我預設一開就時事台。。。。"},{"pid":"fd09f45a72015e9115e0a0a49e27291f8349dc96","tid":1942282,